ico_data.short_desc: Havven is a decentralised payment network and stablecoin. It allows anyone to transact using a stable cryptocurrency.

status_updates.description: Just a reminder that in the next few hours we'll be freezing the system to deploy our scheduled Sirius Release. If anyone still has liquidity in the old sETH pool on Uniswap you'll need to migrate before we begin or your sETH will be frozen! https://blog.synthetix.io/release-scheduled-thursday-september-26/
Here's everything you need to know about our upcoming release on Thursday (AEST). https://blog.synthetix.io/release-scheduled-thursday-september-26/
Here's why you should vote for $sUSD in this week's @compoundfinance community vote! https://blog.synthetix.io/why-susd-should-be-available-for-lending-on-compound/

We just launched two new Index Synths, sCEX and iCEX. These tokens provide long/short exposure to a basket of exchange tokens, $BNB, $LEO, $HT, $OKB, $KCS. https://blog.synthetix.io/introducing-our-first-index-tokens-scex-and-icex/
SNX liquidity has now been added to KyberSwap! https://blog.synthetix.io/snx-liquidity-has-been-added-to-kyberswap/
The system is back up and the first wave of community-governance-led changes are live! More details here: https://blog.synthetix.io/new-synths-750-c-ratio-and-reward-claim-updates/
